data.description: Welcome home! This charming 3-bedroom ranch home invites you in with its classic brick exterior and a concrete driveway leading to a convenient carport. Enjoy lazy afternoons on the new back deck overlooking a shady fenced backyard, complete with Adirondack chairs and a cozy fire pit. Recently remodeled kitchen boasts sleek granite countertops and modern stainless-steel appliances. The original wood floors add warmth and character throughout. Large windows within the home provides generous amount of natural lighting. Primary bedroom features a stylish barn door entrance to the bath. With two storage buildings included within the fenced backyard, you'll have ample space for all your yard maintenance equipment. A partial basement adds versatility to the property as well. Located in a quiet and established neighborhood, this home offers tranquility while being conveniently close to downtown and highway access. Don't miss the opportunity to call 1501 Arrow Wood Road home!
